Comment: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:02.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.32,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回家!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个孩子  羽鸟智世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.76,0:02:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在日本已经被认定为死亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以在这里随便找个地区登记了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.32,0:02:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,麻烦你了  阿道夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.11,0:02:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不  反而要谢谢你告诉我她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,「夜之爱子」可是很珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,有资质和意愿的孩子是宝贵的财产吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是喜欢喝酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.09,0:02:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢和你一起喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.55,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是爱丽丝送的圣诞节礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.75,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只许喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.69,0:02:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们闲着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,托利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么你们两个脸色都这么差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,进来的时候请安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是酒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,让我也来陪你们喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别随便乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手臂还没痊愈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是叫卡达飞尔斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.82,0:03:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后你还有跟他接触过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真好  也介绍给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他是跨世纪的漂流魔术师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,长生不老可是永恒的主题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是无聊的痴梦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是有洁癖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然你很优秀  但是这样会树敌的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,同伴有几个人就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来  来  来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,托利  不能再多喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么  再来一点也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是优秀的话  就不会被那种家伙威胁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况  超有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那种状态还会持续4小时  所以接下来就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况  超麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:05.31,Comment,,0,0,0,,你也来喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,阿道夫  救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况  除了阿道夫还有别人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,梅里托利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.49,0:04:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,妖精?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,它是我老师的使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何  觉得身体没什么重量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,想咳嗽也咳不出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,感受不到冷暖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,请问你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,卡达飞尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字是叫卡达飞尔斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐全身都透明  难道是幽灵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不行  要去你该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.50,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不这样就很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:05:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,卡达…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不叫那个被诅咒的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,卡达飞尔斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.95,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫…约瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,卡达飞尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做我们才能获救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.01,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你去谁那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙…卡达飞尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一直环绕在耳畔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是第几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是睡了两天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.96,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么林德尔家的塞尔克在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你总算醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝  为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我去告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,出了点麻烦  或者说有点不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,衣服随便穿一件就好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,话说爱丽丝你多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,今年18岁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:07:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  智世
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.64,0:08:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,身体怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.38,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,托你的福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,能观察到活着的「夜之爱子」这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能见到你真是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你能活着真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,虽不想承认  但他是我的同辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我代替他向你表示歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是阿道夫·史特劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,之前真是对不住你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是托利·伊尼斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,请叫我托利就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是学院的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,学院?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.99,0:09:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没听他说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,闲话就到这里  赶紧进入正题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,最近在龙之国有幼龙遭到了偷猎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有两头被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,偷猎者在现场留下了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我做的移动装置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.32,0:09:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这次的事情大概是卡达飞尔斯干的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,手臂被夺走的时候似乎连制作方法也一并偷走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这没什么  我很清楚这并不是你的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,问题在于为什么我们要一起去找卡达飞尔斯和幼龙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们跟龙之国的关系很好  而且也亲眼见过卡达飞尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再说了为什么学院要去寻找幼龙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,林德尔大人跟学院之间签有着协定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,跟林德尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕是为了被束缚在那里的友人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,能否帮我们找到幼龙  送回他的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.61,0:10:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一是跟我们无关  二是十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你该不会忘记自己的身体有多脆弱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亚斯才是  该不会是忘记了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你十分疼痛  非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.30,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那个时候?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:10:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正如艾利亚斯说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.71,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有义务就没有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是那些幼龙跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,并不是出于自己的意愿离开龙之国的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,知道曾与我一同玩过的那些孩子遭受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应合作
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微变了点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你们有什么线索或是头绪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,卡达飞尔斯那边毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,幼龙那边就交给林德尔继续追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可能两头龙都意识模糊  现在得不到什么有用的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得卡达飞尔斯应该在伦敦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是我的直觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,史特劳德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,龙很值钱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,当然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  还相当贵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或许会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  谁能把电话借我一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.31,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,原来是您啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,最近怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我现在人在巴黎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是工作的话  会根据报酬和内容来判断是否受理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那边给我更加用力按住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,赛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见  智世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是恩滋华斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法和魔术这些按规定是禁止在拍卖场使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这我有听说  所以我并没有使用魔法和魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,只是把身体从头到尾彻底重组了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,既不是赛门也不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这形象到底是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,关于大家的名字我就不过问了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把这个拿去拍卖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把它排在下午拍卖会的第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这之后才开始正式的拍卖  这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,龙的拍卖将于18点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之前请各位随意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真是什么都有卖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,智世  请收下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,支票和牌板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对于您的卖出价  我们将其一半的钱汇进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.85,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一半的钱吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.39,0:14:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,作为这里曾经的商品以及如今的卖方这是你应得的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,龙十分昂贵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.25,0:14:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,学院的经费要是不够的话  请拿去使用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,钱吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来这本来就是艾利亚斯的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你的气氛完全不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,个头也长高了  跟那时相比简直判若两人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有改变的地方  也有没变的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一个人的核心部分是不会那么容易改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,撇开好坏不谈  你是个十分顽固的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么  你们在聊些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你要来我们这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在家的话  家里会有人寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,立场坚定这是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么想说的就说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你没把学院的事告诉她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子是不会去学院的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有跟她说的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,信使鸟怎么了  是坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,连富烈德这可不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然这么执泥于「夜之爱子」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.02,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是在意「夜之爱子」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,只是担心作为人类的她的将来而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.52,0:15:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就算现在没事  只要她的依存对象还只是你一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那她今后还能成长多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.74,0:16:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有资格说这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.82,0:16:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让走投无路的人背负起知识的金库
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再强行让其登上开往未来的船只
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,假装一副为其指明路的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让对方觉得别无他选
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们其实也没什么区别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,该不会你其实并不想成为魔术师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是被人强迫…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,别擅自决定我的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而且她也是这样期待着的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就看看你们能持续到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,生物是会改变的  无论是否是自己所期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.23,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不过那把骨头完全都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是给别人铺好铁轨让其前行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,结果选择走自己的道路的人比比皆是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是走在自己选择的道路上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我想走哪里  那里就是我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻真好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那么18点的拍卖现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这是来自如今已经锁闭的北方龙之国
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里土生土长的纯翼龙的幼龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那么从80万开始叫价
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,81
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,82
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,85
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,90  90!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,92
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,100
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,学院的极限是150
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,要是超过的话  那时候就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,委托人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,122
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是雇佣的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.01,Comment,,0,0,0,,125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.96,0:18:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是雇佣的人所雇佣过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,125  125
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那个人在看着我们这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,150  有人开价150了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要追价到多少
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,到你所知道的余额上限为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,160
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.25,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,170!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还有客人继续出价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小妹妹  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧  除了你以外谁也听不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.36,0:19:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可以说是正巧给你利用的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,正巧利用…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,180
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,185
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,191
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,193
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,197
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们的资金见底了就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.70,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不行的话  就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我们思念传达的约定  真让人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.88,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,请各位客人千万别让自己后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.68,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人出价吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,260
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,290
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.13,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,290…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,290了  还有更高的价格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是专用的强化咒缚式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.96,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么还能扯开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.19,0:21:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道  这是头一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么看…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,已经发狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,智世
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,它想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还非常厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听到龙的声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  那不是你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.23,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你不需要跟随这股感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.67,0:22:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.98,0:24:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,龙的悲哀咆哮  在伦敦的天空回响着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,为了拯救龙  少女所得出的结论…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是那么的残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.74,0:24:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的  一起回去吧
